heuristically doctors the transcriptions of the CMU&lt;br&gt;
phonetic dictionary. There will be room for errors and inde-&lt;br&gt;
terminacies which will have to be checked against the LPD&lt;br&gt;
by hand, but I could release an alpha version with&lt;br&gt;
uncorrected errors.&lt;br&gt;
