It so happens that I am doing the same thing right now. I have actually
already generated such a dictionary, and it is what I have used to
generate the news. However, I am in the process of creating even a more
accurate dictionary by checking some online sources. (The CMU
dictionary merged Awl and On, whereas the new dictionary will not.)&lt;br&gt;
